Show HN: YouTube/Twitter-like app for capturing insightful moments from YouTube
text:
I have been building an app that makes easy to learn from people you like through manually collected insightful quotes and YouTube videos with no ads and 1-click Bookmarking to allows capture best inspiring moments in video.

Features:

Bookmark YouTube videos with a Click & Save/Revisit/Search for later

Watch YouTube with No Ads.

Watch organized YouTube videos that matters and beneficial to you without getting distracted.

Post your own Quotes + Collect your favorite quotes in bucket

Receive daily push Notifications with Images

And More coming….

Just finished implementing latest features and had a urge to post, so these are not yet updated but you can either join waitlist or try this out, new update coming soon. Still bit slow, buggy and beta.

iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/quotebucket-unique-quotes/id16... Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bayramn.Qu...
